&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Urgent Care + General Practice | No Overnights | Flexible Shifts | Pet Benefits&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Sploot Veterinary Care is redefining urgent and primary care for pets, and we’re seeking a full-time Pet Parent Experience Associate to join our team. This role is ideal for someone who is passionate about delivering exceptional client experiences and making a meaningful impact for pets and their families.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What Makes You A Great Fit&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Veterinary/Operations Experience: Veterinary, animal care, or clinic operations experience preferred, including hands-on work in a veterinary or animal care setting and front-desk/reception responsibilities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Customer Service Excellence: Demonstrated ability to deliver consistently high-quality, client-centered experiences&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Schedule &amp;amp; Availability: Flexible weekly availability, including weekends, for 10-and 12-hour shifts in an onsite role at a dedicated home clinic, with occasional coverage across multiple clinic locations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Client Support &amp;amp; Coordination: Independently serve as the first and last point of contact for pet parents, providing a welcoming, empathetic experience from check-in through check-out&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Schedule Management: Create, manage, and maintain the daily clinic schedule to ensure efficient appointment flow and operational consistency&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Team Collaboration: Partner closely with veterinarians, technicians, and fellow associates to support high-quality patient care&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Problem-Solving: Maintain composure in fast-paced or high-pressure situations, addressing in-clinic needs with professionalism and sound judgment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Clear Communication &amp;amp; Guidance: Reassure and inform pet parents, ensuring they feel confident and supported throughout their visit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Perks of the Pack&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;$20–$22/hour, plus 1.5x pay on Sploot-recognized holidays, with opportunities for growth based on performance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Employee Pet Benefits — free, at-cost, or deep discounts for up to 5 of your own pets&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Health, Dental, and Vision with a generous employer contribution; HSA available&lt;/li&gt;
